# Planning Execution

Use this skill when a task needs explicit decomposition, ordered execution, or careful reconciliation across multiple steps.

Workflow:
- Read `.grove/GROVE.md` first, then `.grove/INDEX.md`.
- Break the task into concrete phases before editing.
- Validate each phase before moving on.
- Prefer parallel work only when write scopes do not overlap.

When to update Grove:
- Record durable workflow or execution guidance in Grove artifacts instead of leaving it only in chat.
